<P>
Photo, Protesters state their opposition to malathion spraying at 6th Street 
and Commonwealth Avenue. ; Photo, KEN LUBAS / Los Angeles Times ; Map, Los 
Angeles County will conduct aerial spraying of malathion tonight, BOB CAREY / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
