<HEADLINE>
<P>
KEATING DONATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In regard to the article (Nov. 23) detailing the donations by Charles Keating 
to various politicians: It seems incredible that Sen. Cranston and this group 
of recipients can stand there and look the taxpayers in the eye and say, "This 
money belongs to me, not the depositor or the bond holder." 
</P>
<P>
As I surmise the situation, the recipients of Mr. Keating's largess, have 
received stolen property, and it should be returned immediately. 
</P>
<P>
GEORGE MOFFAT 
</P>
<P>
La Habra 
