<P>
Photo, Could Kirk Douglas have been giving away secrets about his son Michael 
to Danny DeVito during the post-premiere party? THEODORA LITSIOS; Photo, 
Michael Douglas, Danny DeVito and Kathleen Turner hope for a successful season 
at the box office with "The War of the Roses." The trio worked together in 1984 
hit "Romancing the Stone." 
</P>
