police. ; Photo, Susan Ramage of Orange, Juggert's former girlfriend, with 
their daughter Jenni Sue, the county's Cerebral Palsy poster child. GLENN 
KOENIG / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Steve Juggert began travels after losing job 
when employer went out of business. 
